norswap.violin

Class Stack.DefaultImpls

  • norswap.violin.Stack.DefaultImpls
  • Enclosing interface:
    Stack<T>

    public static class Stack.DefaultImpls

    A fairly classical stack interface, conspicuously missing from both Java and Kotlin stdlibs.
